<article class="env-lemma" id="003V">
  <p><a class="environment-identifier" href="/tag/003V">Lemma <span data-tag="003V">6.2.1</span>.</a> Let $M$ be connected, and let $|\operatorname{Bun}_ G(M)|$ be defined by (<a href="/tag/00EM" data-tag="00EM">6.2.1</a>). Then </p>
  <div class="equation">
  \[  |\operatorname{Bun}_ G(M)|=\sum _{[P]} \frac{1}{|\operatorname{Aut}(P)|}  \]
</div>
  <p> where the sum is taken over isomorphism classes in $\operatorname{Bun}_ G(M)$. </p>
</article>